  "4302760": {
    "name": "Armita's Search",
    "steam_appid": 4302760,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带领阿尔米塔穿越残酷的废土，在回合制战术卡牌战斗中奋战，并做出塑造她的人性——以及结局——的选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Raiders World: Armita’s Search》是一款剧情驱动的单人战术 roguelite 卡牌游戏，背景设定在末日后的世界：在废土中保持善良，是最难的一条路。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>善良是困难模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的决定改变的不只是对白——还会改变可用行动、世界对待你的方式，以及结局。保持人性，就要付出高昂代价。或者让自己变得冷硬，成为掠夺者——那样更容易活下去。废土里最重要的资源不是战利品、不是子弹，甚至也不是净水。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>最重要的资源……是人性。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/183308dddf1b1ea71b11515bdfe888fc.poster.avif?t=1771683669\" aria-label=\"Raiders World: Armita&#039;s Search — Humanity\" width=1170 height=1217 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/183308dddf1b1ea71b11515bdfe888fc.webm?t=1771683669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在废土中“养大”阿尔米塔</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿尔米塔在隐秘的地堡里安全长大——直到巡逻队闯入并绑走了她的父亲。身边只剩下保姆机器人兼保镖弗雷德，她踏上穿越废土的旅程——一个一半被外星人改造地貌、一半被野蛮幸存者烧毁与洗劫的世界。道路会改变阿尔米塔，而你的选择将决定她能否找回家人、揭开末日真相——更重要的是，她最终会变成什么样的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/b75d620e1e8d84e02f73c16d1c46d710.poster.avif?t=1771683669\" aria-label=\"Raiders World: Armita&#039;s Search — Story Event\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/b75d620e1e8d84e02f73c16d1c46d710.webm?t=1771683669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/b75d620e1e8d84e02f73c16d1c46d710.mp4?t=1771683669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>（不）是废土英雄</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入你的同伴不只是战场上的“挨打工具人”，也不只是带来新机制的卡牌包。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们有故事，会讲自己的经历；有性格，有显性与隐性的目标，未必与你一致；会对你的人性等级与选择做出反应。他们也会像你一样，在废土中生存、改变、甚至死去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/68c7b1796c9a9c5e06257a220012fbb1.poster.avif?t=1771683669\" aria-label=\"Raiders World: Armita&#039;s Search — Companions\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/68c7b1796c9a9c5e06257a220012fbb1.webm?t=1771683669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/68c7b1796c9a9c5e06257a220012fbb1.mp4?t=1771683669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>风格化 2D 废土</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手绘 2D 世界，粗粝的漫画气质与阴郁氛围——机制、卡牌与剧情都指向同一个问题：当你穿越废土后，你会变成什么样的人？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/6ed96a2eabbf8434cef56babbbfa2509.poster.avif?t=1771683669\" aria-label=\"Raiders World: Armita&#039;s Search — Combat\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/6ed96a2eabbf8434cef56babbbfa2509.webm?t=1771683669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/6ed96a2eabbf8434cef56babbbfa2509.mp4?t=1771683669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>每个区域一副新牌组</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >废土被划分为多个区域，每个区域都以一次快速配装开局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个区域开始时，只需三步选择：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 阿尔米塔的预设（随着她成长与道德路线变化解锁更多）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 两名同伴（随着剧情推进与随机遭遇解锁更多）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个预设与同伴都会带来 3 张标志性卡牌，因此你将以一副小而定制的 12 张牌组开启该区域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你无法通关该区域，就会回滚到区域起点重新构筑：换一个预设、换一批同伴，并针对该区域的敌人与 Boss 制定新策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/2eb56c3fc88fe10a5bf299a264cdc95c.poster.avif?t=1771683669\" aria-label=\"Raiders World: Armita&#039;s Search — Start Deck\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/2eb56c3fc88fe10a5bf299a264cdc95c.webm?t=1771683669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/2eb56c3fc88fe10a5bf299a264cdc95c.mp4?t=1771683669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>三种卡牌：同伴、物品、麻烦</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >旅途中你会获得：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 同伴卡——有名字的角色。若资源足够雇佣，他们不会孤身加入，而是携带一套 4 张“迷你牌组”（同伴 + 3 张标志性卡），并保证内部联动</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 物品卡——拥有独特机制的武器与工具；组出组合，为 Boss 做准备</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 麻烦卡——口渴、故障、辐射、疾病等困境，会让战斗更难。你会想办法把它们清除掉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/4c9693052c0a190f9d2805cdc4ab390d.poster.avif?t=1771683669\" aria-label=\"Raiders World: Armita&#039;s Search — Many Cards\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/4c9693052c0a190f9d2805cdc4ab390d.webm?t=1771683669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/4c9693052c0a190f9d2805cdc4ab390d.mp4?t=1771683669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>奖励思考的回合制战术</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗是战术向回合制，强调规划而非反应：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 双方最多各 5 名战斗单位</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 友方与敌方都会在回合结束时自动攻击</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 他们会提前“预告意图”，你有整整一回合来应对</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 多种攻击模式（近战、射击、范围攻击、增益与减益）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 掩体是不会立刻消失的临时防护</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 敌人分波次登场并有队长：你可以集火队长让小队溃逃，或先清理杂兵来削弱队长</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/ef8ee2c26bbf1062c766bc23bc58c312.poster.avif?t=1771683669\" aria-label=\"Raiders World: Armita&#039;s Search — Chase Combat\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/ef8ee2c26bbf1062c766bc23bc58c312.webm?t=1771683669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/ef8ee2c26bbf1062c766bc23bc58c312.mp4?t=1771683669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>资源与道路</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在废土中的每一次移动都会消耗资源。若资源不足，你的牌组会被“麻烦卡”填满——战斗胜利将变得更困难。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/6df4fe427d67ddd5fb8586fde0b68de4.poster.avif?t=1771683669\" aria-label=\"Raiders World: Armita&#039;s Search — Troubles\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/6df4fe427d67ddd5fb8586fde0b68de4.webm?t=1771683669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/6df4fe427d67ddd5fb8586fde0b68de4.mp4?t=1771683669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有时你会遇到有护卫的商人：你可以交易——也可以在你的人性足够低时选择抢劫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/7e8f197ec99dee29a9a2cfcb894df76f.avif?t=1771683669\" alt=\"Raiders World: Armita&#039;s Search — Regiones\" width=1560 height=558 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>可重复游玩的内容</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次尝试通关某个区域，都会是故事、敌人与后果的全新组合：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 些关键剧情事件必定出现，但会随你的选择与人性变化而改变</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 每个区域的首领与小首领属于固定阵营，但会用不同队伍迎战你</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 区域内相当一部分事件与战斗会随机抽取，但只属于该区域</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 随着阿尔米塔成长与路线演变解锁新的预设</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 解锁新的同伴及其迷你牌组</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 不同路线、遭遇与区域结果</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 根据你的决策与人性等级解锁多个结局</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧情事件构成战役主干，而额外遭遇、战斗与随机事件则带来更多变数、资源与风险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/09fa40ec6d9af26cdca6a050bbb61990.avif?t=1771683669\" alt=\"Raiders World: Armita&#039;s Search — Armita Adult\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >------------------------------------------------------------</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RAIDERS WORLD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raiders World 不只是一个游戏——它是一个完整的原创世界观。早在 2017 年，我们就推出了以这个世界为背景的桌游。现在，我们正在准备发布剧情向卡组构筑游戏《Armita’s Search》。之后我们计划推出：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 设定在该世界观中的桌面 RPG，你将能扮演一名掠夺者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 一部漫画，讲述女武神 Beth 和 迅捷 在名为 地壳 的荒原地区展开的冒险</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— 另外两款不同类型的电子游戏，继续讲述这个世界的故事</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/7821d093f09c4fefba3adcd03d3e6d3d.avif?t=1771683669\" width=570 height=286 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你会守住人性——还是成为这些伤痕累累土地上的新恐怖？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4302760/extras/22c9e7166d314eb69b63509628bf7184.avif?t=1771683669\" alt=\"Raiders World: Armita&#039;s Search — Main Art\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
